      "ruleId": "hz.web.eb212e096e9235b7.rule.1",
      "text": "The trick is always how do these apps authenticate the user or obtain a token they can use to access those APIs.</p>\\n<p>This post details a few specific challenges with OAuth preventing it from being used by independent websites, as well as the solutions to each.</p>\\n\\n<h2>Client Registration</h2>\\n<p>The first major hurdle to overcome is the need for the developer to register to get API keys for the service.",
